OL,3,CCumbria set for elected mayor after
OL,4,Ccouncil approval
OL,6,FCumbria is set to get an elected mayor
OL,7,Ffor the first time ever after both
OL,8,FCumberland Council and Westmorland and
OL,9,FFurness Council approved plans.
OL,11,FBoth councils held meetings on Tuesday
OL,12,Fmorning in Carlisle and Kendal.
OL,14,FThe first mayoral election is due to
OL,15,Ftake place in May 2027 which will be
OL,16,Fin-line with local council elections.
OL,17,FThe combined authority for the mayor
OL,18,Fwill be set-up in either April or May
OL,19,Fof 2026.
