OL,3,CCumbria set for elected mayor after
OL,4,Ccouncil approval
OL,6,FThe new mayor and authority will have
OL,7,Fa range of powers including transport,
OL,8,Finfrastructure, housing, employment,
OL,9,Feconomic development and regeneration,
OL,10,Fenvironment, climate change, health
OL,11,Fand public safety.
OL,13,FThe powers for the mayor will be in
OL,14,Faddition to what is already controlled
OL,15,Fby Cumberland Council and Westmorland
OL,16,Fand Furness Council.
